{
  "stem": "2004.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are going through Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are going through Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Usually, when we traveled through Poland-- now, here we could observe a lot of things because we were in an open car.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could observe the reaction of the local population.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Any time we would-- while we were going through Poland, you know, we want-- you go from Poland to Austria, you travel part Poland, then part Czechoslovakia, then you come into Austria.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "While we were traveling through Poland, we were getting dirty looks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They knew we were Jews because we had our star of David and all that sort of thing on our-- on our striped uniforms.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And however, when we travelled to Czechoslovakia, we were getting much more sympathetic looks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I remember one incident.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The train stopped in Czechoslovakia, and there were some old ladies that came to the train, and they saw us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they started throwing bread at us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were throwing bread at us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, I've never experienced anything like this, where the local population was throwing bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, here they were now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was forbidden, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there were Germans standing there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And each time one of these women came close and threw bread, with a butt of the rifle, they were hitting-- they were getting hit with the butt of the rifle.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They weren't shooting them, but they were hitting-- they were hitting them with the butt of the rifles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now, these people, knowing very well that they were going to be injured, they really risked their lives.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were throwing bread at us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, I can-- I can appreciate anything like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So at the-- at the-- at the-- the fear was there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
